{"tid":711452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從「天下圍攻」眾籌足見黃屍港豬有幾撚蠢","createTime":"2018-06-21T14:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T04:17:17.000Z","uid":73883,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9e45cc278d686562b73e8713d6debfd96299a166","tid":711452,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/220800_3efcb75d4e6cd090336214424f8d5076.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F220800_3efcb75d4e6cd090336214424f8d5076.png&h=f6f9b1e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n籌左 223 萬Admin + 拍片 + credit card 手續費已經用撚左 32 萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成立個監管委員會睇住盤數，但又係自己泛民友，民主黨副主席羅健熙、梁家傑、莫乃光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6118e5b0d8c941017a787c55bdd846bedba0fec","tid":711452,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:21:59.000Z","msg":"VIDEO PRODUCTION 係咪自己友公司做返?"},{"pid":"eb65bd33cb2f73c3dd40eff22149acd7a62c1d6b","tid":711452,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f6118e5b0d8c941017a787c55bdd846bedba0fec","tid":711452,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:21:59.000Z","msg":"VIDEO PRODUCTION 係咪自己友公司做返?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:30:41.000Z","msg":"監管委員會都自己人圍威喂，你話呢？<br />\n<br />\n仲有搞左兩三個月就已經用左筆款項嘅 5% 做 admin fee，但班黃屍港豬完全唔覺有問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8899f88d0a8e22424cefa3e197af6c10e3ab45f3","tid":711452,"uid":180459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-2